1
00:00:06,380 --> 00:00:07,360
<font color="yellow">(Episode 35)</font>

2
00:00:07,360 --> 00:00:09,990
<font color="yellow">- It was nice to meet you all.
-  Thank you.</font>

3
00:00:16,590 --> 00:00:19,520
<font color="yellow">Oh, thank you.</font>

4
00:00:35,160 --> 00:00:36,160
<font color="yellow">Congratulations, Uncle.</font>

5
00:00:38,190 --> 00:00:39,520
<font color="yellow">I'll visit you in prison.</font>

6
00:00:44,460 --> 00:00:45,860
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

7
00:00:51,060 --> 00:00:52,360
<font color="yellow">Byun Il Jae.</font>

8
00:00:52,360 --> 00:00:54,890
<font color="yellow">You're under arrest for violating election laws.</font>

9
00:00:56,660 --> 00:00:57,660
<font color="yellow">Honey!</font>

10
00:01:05,060 --> 00:01:06,260
<font color="yellow">This is the teaser.</font>

11
00:01:07,060 --> 00:01:08,260
<font color="yellow">There's more to come.</font>

12
00:01:10,290 --> 00:01:14,790
<font color="yellow">Murder, abduction, illegal slush funds and more.</font>

13
00:01:20,160 --> 00:01:21,360
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan, how dare you...</font>

14
00:01:26,660 --> 00:01:27,870
<font color="yellow">Honey.</font>

15
00:01:27,870 --> 00:01:28,890
<font color="yellow">Honey!</font>

16
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:40,790
<font color="yellow">Now he's cheating children as well.</font>

17
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:42,760
<font color="yellow">There's still a long way to go...</font>

18
00:01:43,620 --> 00:01:44,820
<font color="yellow">in order to reveal his true self.</font>

19
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:56,860
<font color="yellow">Do you admit to the contents of the recording released on broadcast?</font>

20
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:59,060
<font color="yellow">I haven't seen the broadcast yet.</font>

21
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:01,620
<font color="yellow">Cho Cham, the candidate that supported you,</font>

22
00:02:01,620 --> 00:02:03,930
<font color="yellow">confessed to the prosecution that he received bribery.</font>

23
00:02:03,930 --> 00:02:05,230
<font color="yellow">Is that so?</font>

24
00:02:05,230 --> 00:02:07,590
<font color="yellow">That means this incident must be...</font>

25
00:02:07,590 --> 00:02:09,560
<font color="yellow">a political conspiracy.</font>

26
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,550
<font color="yellow">Are you saying someone is trying to frame you?</font>

27
00:02:11,550 --> 00:02:14,920
<font color="yellow">There is no way he would say that otherwise.</font>

28
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:17,090
<font color="yellow">You've been elected as the mayor of Seoul.</font>

29
00:02:17,090 --> 00:02:18,120
<font color="yellow">Please comment.</font>

30
00:02:19,490 --> 00:02:22,420
<font color="yellow">For all the Seoul citizens who have given...</font>

31
00:02:22,420 --> 00:02:24,160
<font color="yellow">their precious votes to me,</font>

32
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:27,890
<font color="yellow">I will fight against all of these suspicions...</font>

33
00:02:27,890 --> 00:02:31,080
<font color="yellow">and conspiracies until the end. Please watch me.</font>

34
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:32,160
<font color="yellow">Please move out of the way.</font>

35
00:02:33,090 --> 00:02:35,890
<font color="yellow">Are you saying that you're innocent? Are you?</font>

36
00:02:35,890 --> 00:02:37,420
<font color="yellow">Please give us an answer.</font>

37
00:02:54,260 --> 00:02:57,320
<font color="yellow">Why are you so surprised? Did you see a ghost or something?</font>

38
00:03:00,820 --> 00:03:03,460
<font color="yellow">Are you surprised to see someone...</font>

39
00:03:03,860 --> 00:03:04,960
<font color="yellow">you thought was dead?</font>

40
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:10,060
<font color="yellow">I'm Oh Soo Yeon.</font>

41
00:03:10,420 --> 00:03:12,990
<font color="yellow">The one you tried to kidnap and murder.</font>

42
00:03:16,190 --> 00:03:20,020
<font color="yellow">I was wondering who would frame me,</font>

43
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:22,290
<font color="yellow">but it must have been you and Gi Tan.</font>

44
00:03:22,290 --> 00:03:24,260
<font color="yellow">Say that in the interrogation room.</font>

45
00:03:24,790 --> 00:03:27,020
<font color="yellow">The more you talk about the past,</font>

46
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,460
<font color="yellow">the better it is for us.</font>

47
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:32,190
<font color="yellow">My brother and Gi Tan's parents...</font>

48
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:34,190
<font color="yellow">Right, there's one more.</font>

49
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:36,420
<font color="yellow">Your late wife.</font>

50
00:03:38,290 --> 00:03:41,090
<font color="yellow">Once the world finds out what you did to those people,</font>

51
00:03:41,090 --> 00:03:42,120
<font color="yellow">you'll never...</font>

52
00:03:42,620 --> 00:03:44,320
<font color="yellow">see the light of day again.</font>

53
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,090
<font color="yellow">A lawyer...</font>

54
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:50,220
<font color="yellow">should be more careful with her words.</font>

55
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:53,690
<font color="yellow">You should only say things you can be responsible for.</font>

56
00:03:54,390 --> 00:03:55,860
<font color="yellow">Okay, Lawyer Oh?</font>

57
00:03:55,860 --> 00:03:58,320
<font color="yellow">If it's bothering you, sue me for defamation.</font>

58
00:03:58,760 --> 00:04:00,020
<font color="yellow">That's what I prefer.</font>

59
00:04:02,220 --> 00:04:05,590
<font color="yellow">That's enough, Lawyer Oh. You'll scare the detective.</font>

60
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,190
<font color="yellow">Poor thing.</font>

61
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:11,520
<font color="yellow">He doesn't have any honour left to be ruined.</font>

62
00:04:12,260 --> 00:04:14,460
<font color="yellow">How can he sue you for defamation?</font>

63
00:04:15,620 --> 00:04:17,990
<font color="yellow">Are you going to keep listening to them?</font>

64
00:04:20,990 --> 00:04:21,990
<font color="yellow">Let's go.</font>

65
00:04:34,330 --> 00:04:36,720
<font color="yellow">We're late. I have to go see Cho Cham.</font>

66
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:40,170
<font color="yellow">Can you find out how it's going at the prosecutor's office?</font>

67
00:04:40,170 --> 00:04:41,260
<font color="yellow">Why?</font>

68
00:04:41,260 --> 00:04:43,790
<font color="yellow">We should find out what his prosecutor is like.</font>

69
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:48,690
<font color="yellow">Okay. I'll put in a call. Go to the fifth floor...</font>

70
00:04:48,690 --> 00:04:50,590
<font color="yellow">and ask for Detective Yang Jin Soo.</font>

71
00:04:51,060 --> 00:04:53,990
<font color="yellow">He's the informant here, so he'll tell you almost everything.</font>

72
00:04:53,990 --> 00:04:54,990
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

73
00:04:55,830 --> 00:04:56,860
<font color="yellow">Let's go.</font>

74
00:04:58,330 --> 00:05:01,660
<font color="yellow">Seoul Mayor Byun Il Jae claimed innocence,</font>

75
00:05:01,660 --> 00:05:04,690
<font color="yellow">but the prosecution is said to have already acquired...</font>

76
00:05:04,690 --> 00:05:08,280
<font color="yellow">the confession of the independent candidate Cho Cham...</font>

77
00:05:08,280 --> 00:05:09,620
<font color="yellow">Will Gun Woo be all right?</font>

78
00:05:10,260 --> 00:05:11,260
<font color="yellow">He has...</font>

79
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:15,060
<font color="yellow">the support from the shareholders thanks to Il Jae.</font>

80
00:05:18,690 --> 00:05:20,160
<font color="yellow">You make no sense.</font>

81
00:05:20,790 --> 00:05:23,500
<font color="yellow">Why would Gun Woo and Il Jae part ways because of Soo Yeon?</font>

82
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:24,890
<font color="yellow">I'm sure of it.</font>

83
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:31,620
<font color="yellow">The EGM is around the corner. Gun Woo would never do this.</font>

84
00:05:31,990 --> 00:05:33,020
<font color="yellow">Anyway,</font>

85
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:34,960
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo...</font>

86
00:05:35,490 --> 00:05:37,590
<font color="yellow">is nothing but a bird without wings.</font>

87
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:45,620
<font color="yellow">I just got a call from the secretary's office.</font>

88
00:05:45,620 --> 00:05:47,790
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo is holding a dinner with the shareholders.</font>

89
00:05:48,690 --> 00:05:49,930
<font color="yellow">See?</font>

90
00:05:49,930 --> 00:05:51,490
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo must be nervous.</font>

91
00:05:51,490 --> 00:05:53,920
<font color="yellow">That's why he's meeting with the shareholders.</font>

92
00:05:55,390 --> 00:05:57,850
<font color="yellow">Get me the list of attendees for the dinner.</font>

93
00:05:57,850 --> 00:05:59,390
<font color="yellow">I'll call them myself.</font>

94
00:05:59,390 --> 00:06:00,420
<font color="yellow">Yes, Ma'am.</font>

95
00:06:02,620 --> 00:06:06,160
<font color="yellow">Those disloyal shareholders are trying to flatter Gun Woo.</font>

96
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:08,010
<font color="yellow">I don't like them.</font>

97
00:06:08,010 --> 00:06:11,340
<font color="yellow">Even if you don't like them, it's time for a carrot, not a stick.</font>

98
00:06:11,340 --> 00:06:13,160
<font color="yellow">Don't even think about losing your temper.</font>

99
00:06:13,820 --> 00:06:15,790
<font color="yellow">The sun is right above us.</font>

100
00:06:15,790 --> 00:06:18,920
<font color="yellow">What are you scared of? We should say whatever we want.</font>

101
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,990
<font color="yellow">History changes...</font>

102
00:06:20,490 --> 00:06:23,290
<font color="yellow">not because of the loyal subjects but because of the disloyal ones.</font>

103
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:24,920
<font color="yellow">You'll see.</font>

104
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:28,220
<font color="yellow">They'll be the ones that help us take over Dodo Group.</font>

105
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:31,520
<font color="yellow">Wow. My mum became so smart...</font>

106
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:33,720
<font color="yellow">after becoming the chairwoman.</font>

107
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,520
<font color="yellow">Do you think your father was so smart to begin with?</font>

108
00:06:35,860 --> 00:06:37,690
<font color="yellow">The position makes the person.</font>

109
00:06:48,390 --> 00:06:49,420
<font color="yellow">Mum.</font>

110
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:51,390
<font color="yellow">It's Gun Woo.</font>

111
00:06:53,860 --> 00:06:55,060
<font color="yellow">Where are the shareholders?</font>

112
00:06:55,060 --> 00:06:57,360
<font color="yellow">They're already in our room.</font>

113
00:07:16,590 --> 00:07:18,590
<font color="yellow">The shareholders are in a different room.</font>

114
00:07:19,220 --> 00:07:21,160
<font color="yellow">What do you mean? It was supposed to be here.</font>

115
00:07:22,260 --> 00:07:24,820
<font color="yellow">Chairwoman Hwang snatched them away.</font>

116
00:07:29,660 --> 00:07:31,090
<font color="yellow">Where are they meeting?</font>

117
00:07:36,060 --> 00:07:37,060
<font color="yellow">You all heard that...</font>

118
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:40,760
<font color="yellow">Chairman Do can't move around...</font>

119
00:07:41,290 --> 00:07:42,630
<font color="yellow">without his wheelchair, right?</font>

120
00:07:42,630 --> 00:07:43,760
<font color="yellow">Is it that bad?</font>

121
00:07:44,260 --> 00:07:47,160
<font color="yellow">I heard that he'll be participating in the next EGM.</font>

122
00:07:47,890 --> 00:07:49,460
<font color="yellow">Of course he would like to.</font>

123
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:51,620
<font color="yellow">But he collapsed just a few days ago...</font>

124
00:07:52,190 --> 00:07:53,690
<font color="yellow">and was sent to the hospital.</font>

125
00:07:57,820 --> 00:08:01,090
<font color="yellow">All right. I won't take long.</font>

126
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:05,260
<font color="yellow">Raise your hands if you agree...</font>

127
00:08:06,020 --> 00:08:08,060
<font color="yellow">on dismissing Vice Chairman Do during the EGM.</font>

128
00:08:12,020 --> 00:08:13,160
<font color="yellow">Listen.</font>

129
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,720
<font color="yellow">Can't you see that things have changed?</font>

130
00:08:17,590 --> 00:08:21,260
<font color="yellow">If you want to extend your contracts, you should be wise.</font>

131
00:08:21,690 --> 00:08:24,790
<font color="yellow">Well... What about Director Byun?</font>

132
00:08:24,790 --> 00:08:26,190
<font color="yellow">Director Byun...</font>

133
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:28,690
<font color="yellow">had a falling out with Vice Chairman Do.</font>

134
00:08:29,660 --> 00:08:31,830
<font color="yellow">Is that true?</font>

135
00:08:31,830 --> 00:08:35,820
<font color="yellow">Why would I make things up?</font>

136
00:08:43,890 --> 00:08:44,930
<font color="yellow">Vice Chairman Do.</font>

137
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:46,820
<font color="yellow">What do you think you're doing?</font>

138
00:08:47,220 --> 00:08:48,490
<font color="yellow">That's what I'd like to ask.</font>

139
00:08:48,490 --> 00:08:51,020
<font color="yellow">These people had a meeting with me. Why did you snatch them away?</font>

140
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,960
<font color="yellow">Do you think...</font>

141
00:08:54,390 --> 00:08:56,300
<font color="yellow">I dragged them over here?</font>

142
00:08:56,300 --> 00:08:57,960
<font color="yellow">They came on their own will.</font>

143
00:08:58,430 --> 00:09:00,990
<font color="yellow">Chairwoman, don't get so upset.</font>

144
00:09:00,990 --> 00:09:03,960
<font color="yellow">Since Vice Chairman Do is here,</font>

145
00:09:04,290 --> 00:09:05,820
<font color="yellow">why don't you check?</font>

146
00:09:06,590 --> 00:09:09,660
<font color="yellow">Is it true that you and Director Byun had a falling out?</font>

147
00:09:14,260 --> 00:09:15,960
<font color="yellow">Don't bother lying.</font>

148
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:17,930
<font color="yellow">It'll make you look pathetic.</font>

149
00:09:22,160 --> 00:09:23,160
<font color="yellow">It's true.</font>

150
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:32,820
<font color="yellow">All right. Let me ask you again.</font>

151
00:09:33,430 --> 00:09:35,960
<font color="yellow">Raise your hands if you agree...</font>

152
00:09:36,460 --> 00:09:38,090
<font color="yellow">on dismissing Vice Chairman Do during the EGM.</font>

153
00:09:45,520 --> 00:09:48,430
<font color="yellow">Hey! Is that up or down?</font>

154
00:09:52,160 --> 00:09:53,350
<font color="yellow">All right, all right.</font>

155
00:09:53,350 --> 00:09:57,760
<font color="yellow">We can gather at the EGM with our chairwoman in the lead.</font>

156
00:10:00,490 --> 00:10:01,720
<font color="yellow">For Chairwoman Hwang!</font>

157
00:10:04,930 --> 00:10:05,960
<font color="yellow">Vice Chairman Do.</font>

158
00:10:06,620 --> 00:10:08,220
<font color="yellow">Are you going to stay there?</font>

159
00:10:08,860 --> 00:10:10,290
<font color="yellow">You're making everyone uncomfortable.</font>

160
00:10:20,020 --> 00:10:21,060
<font color="yellow">Hey, Gun Woo.</font>

161
00:10:25,860 --> 00:10:26,890
<font color="yellow">Did you see that?</font>

162
00:10:27,430 --> 00:10:30,320
<font color="yellow">You're nothing without Il Jae.</font>

163
00:10:31,460 --> 00:10:34,960
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon will just use you and abandon you, too.</font>

164
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:37,190
<font color="yellow">It doesn't matter what happens between Il Jae and me.</font>

165
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:40,790
<font color="yellow">Dodo Group is my father's company and it's where I work.</font>

166
00:10:41,820 --> 00:10:43,890
<font color="yellow">Are you still lost?</font>

167
00:10:44,260 --> 00:10:45,260
<font color="yellow">Hey!</font>

168
00:10:46,220 --> 00:10:49,220
<font color="yellow">Dodo Group is mine. I'm the heir.</font>

169
00:10:49,620 --> 00:10:51,590
<font color="yellow">Only the people I approve of will be working here.</font>

170
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:58,160
<font color="yellow">That's why you should just get lost.</font>

171
00:10:59,020 --> 00:11:02,060
<font color="yellow">Stop embarrassing the family. Do you understand?</font>

172
00:11:11,660 --> 00:11:13,560
<font color="yellow">Shouldn't Lawyer Oh know about this?</font>

173
00:11:16,220 --> 00:11:19,060
<font color="yellow">She should know what kind of trouble you put yourself in to help...</font>

174
00:11:19,060 --> 00:11:21,060
<font color="yellow">It was my decision so I should deal with it myself.</font>

175
00:11:22,260 --> 00:11:23,890
<font color="yellow">Don't say anything to Soo Yeon.</font>

176
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,320
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

177
00:11:28,390 --> 00:11:30,560
<font color="yellow">Gwi Ja and Gwang Woo.</font>

178
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:33,320
<font color="yellow">You should've left while I was still nice.</font>

179
00:11:42,420 --> 00:11:44,790
<font color="yellow">I couldn't have been taken down like this...</font>

180
00:11:45,420 --> 00:11:47,720
<font color="yellow">without a traitor inside.</font>

181
00:11:49,260 --> 00:11:51,760
<font color="yellow">Before that, I have to prepare something.</font>

182
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:54,680
<font color="yellow">Money and trust.</font>

183
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:57,300
<font color="yellow">- Trust?
-  Without trust,</font>

184
00:11:57,300 --> 00:11:58,790
<font color="yellow">this scheme will fail.</font>

185
00:11:59,220 --> 00:12:01,620
<font color="yellow">How much do you trust me?</font>

186
00:12:02,220 --> 00:12:04,860
<font color="yellow">How much do I have to trust you?</font>

187
00:12:04,860 --> 00:12:05,990
<font color="yellow">Completely.</font>

188
00:12:08,490 --> 00:12:09,520
<font color="yellow">Could it be?</font>

189
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,660
<font color="yellow">Could the traitor be...</font>

190
00:12:11,990 --> 00:12:13,120
<font color="yellow">Chae Ryung?</font>

191
00:12:19,760 --> 00:12:21,220
<font color="yellow">You don't have much time, Sir.</font>

192
00:12:21,620 --> 00:12:22,660
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

193
00:12:26,420 --> 00:12:27,600
<font color="yellow">Are you okay?</font>

194
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:29,560
<font color="yellow">Call my father-in-law first.</font>

195
00:12:46,520 --> 00:12:48,320
<font color="yellow">Yes, Mr Oh.</font>

196
00:12:49,160 --> 00:12:50,360
<font color="yellow">It's me, Father.</font>

197
00:12:51,220 --> 00:12:53,760
<font color="yellow">I have a favour to ask you.</font>

198
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:55,120
<font color="yellow">Hang up.</font>

199
00:12:55,620 --> 00:12:56,830
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

200
00:12:56,830 --> 00:12:59,390
<font color="yellow">I have no intention of helping you,</font>

201
00:12:59,820 --> 00:13:01,760
<font color="yellow">so don't even think about it!</font>

202
00:13:03,160 --> 00:13:04,990
<font color="yellow">Who was that?</font>

203
00:13:06,160 --> 00:13:07,590
<font color="yellow">Il Jae.</font>

204
00:13:07,590 --> 00:13:08,620
<font color="yellow">Father.</font>

205
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:11,590
<font color="yellow">Won't you really help Il Jae at all?</font>

206
00:13:11,590 --> 00:13:13,990
<font color="yellow">I told you, I've abandoned him.</font>

207
00:13:15,060 --> 00:13:16,890
<font color="yellow">Don't make me repeat things.</font>

208
00:13:18,860 --> 00:13:20,190
<font color="yellow">Father.</font>

209
00:13:20,190 --> 00:13:21,220
<font color="yellow">Ma'am.</font>

210
00:13:22,420 --> 00:13:23,790
<font color="yellow">Let him be alone.</font>

211
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:28,890
<font color="yellow">He's like that because he's upset.</font>

212
00:13:29,220 --> 00:13:32,160
<font color="yellow">Once he calms down, he'll help Mayor Byun.</font>

213
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:42,570
<font color="yellow">My father-in-law is treating me like an abandoned child.</font>

214
00:13:42,570 --> 00:13:43,590
