<font color="yellow">I can tell who's behind this.</font>

427
00:27:49,820 --> 00:27:52,160
<font color="yellow">- Pardon?
-  A sudden investigation...</font>

428
00:27:52,790 --> 00:27:54,320
<font color="yellow">on tax evasion and illegal lobbying?</font>

429
00:27:54,690 --> 00:27:56,460
<font color="yellow">Are you saying that it's Il Jae's doing?</font>

430
00:27:56,860 --> 00:27:58,090
<font color="yellow">I'm almost certain about this.</font>

431
00:27:58,590 --> 00:27:59,960
<font color="yellow">Don't worry and just go back to the office.</font>

432
00:28:01,390 --> 00:28:02,390
<font color="yellow">Let me make a call.</font>

433
00:28:06,790 --> 00:28:07,790
<font color="yellow">It's me, Father.</font>

434
00:28:09,020 --> 00:28:10,690
<font color="yellow">There's a problem with the business.</font>

435
00:28:21,190 --> 00:28:23,690
<font color="yellow">Look who it is. It's Gi Tan.</font>

436
00:28:25,590 --> 00:28:29,360
<font color="yellow">Chief Prosecutor Ko, why are these people here?</font>

437
00:28:29,360 --> 00:28:30,520
<font color="yellow">They were charged...</font>

438
00:28:31,390 --> 00:28:33,360
<font color="yellow">on suspicion of illegal lobbying.</font>

439
00:28:40,520 --> 00:28:43,820
<font color="yellow">I'm on my way out after getting my leave without detention.</font>

440
00:28:45,320 --> 00:28:48,290
<font color="yellow">This is what one's power can do.</font>

441
00:28:50,020 --> 00:28:53,920
<font color="yellow">I'm not the same man who used to crawl at your aunt's feet.</font>

442
00:28:55,890 --> 00:28:57,690
<font color="yellow">You're trying to reveal my corrupted doings?</font>

443
00:28:58,690 --> 00:29:00,960
<font color="yellow">Once I start my term as the Seoul Mayor,</font>

444
00:29:01,890 --> 00:29:04,520
<font color="yellow">you won't even get to see me eye to eye, Guk Cheol.</font>

445
00:29:08,360 --> 00:29:10,560
<font color="yellow">Chief. We just received...</font>

446
00:29:10,560 --> 00:29:12,260
<font color="yellow">a call from the Chinese Consulate.</font>

447
00:29:21,690 --> 00:29:23,160
<font color="yellow">The charge has been dismissed,</font>

448
00:29:23,720 --> 00:29:25,020
<font color="yellow">so you may leave.</font>

449
00:29:26,490 --> 00:29:27,720
<font color="yellow">Are you Chief Prosecutor Ko?</font>

450
00:29:28,790 --> 00:29:29,790
<font color="yellow">We will be looking into...</font>

451
00:29:30,290 --> 00:29:32,190
<font color="yellow">this incident in detail.</font>

452
00:29:32,590 --> 00:29:33,590
<font color="yellow">My apologies.</font>

453
00:29:34,160 --> 00:29:35,890
<font color="yellow">There must have been a mistake.</font>

454
00:29:36,460 --> 00:29:37,860
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

455
00:29:38,590 --> 00:29:39,690
<font color="yellow">Power, you say?</font>

456
00:29:40,820 --> 00:29:43,220
<font color="yellow">I'm not the same Guk Cheol you used to know.</font>

457
00:29:44,890 --> 00:29:46,790
<font color="yellow">It's an eye for an eye.</font>

458
00:29:47,590 --> 00:29:48,860
<font color="yellow">I'll put up a good fight,</font>

459
00:29:50,790 --> 00:29:51,790
<font color="yellow">so get yourself ready.</font>

460
00:30:04,060 --> 00:30:06,020
<font color="yellow">What happened?</font>

461
00:30:07,120 --> 00:30:08,660
<font color="yellow">A complaint came into...</font>

462
00:30:08,660 --> 00:30:10,690
<font color="yellow">the Chinese consulate through a high office in China.</font>

463
00:30:11,890 --> 00:30:13,390
<font color="yellow">We don't have enough evidence.</font>

464
00:30:14,260 --> 00:30:16,620
<font color="yellow">If this gets out of hand, we'll be the one in trouble.</font>

465
00:31:05,160 --> 00:31:06,190
<font color="yellow">I'm glad you're out.</font>

466
00:31:10,220 --> 00:31:12,290
<font color="yellow">I was hoping you'd come.</font>

467
00:31:12,690 --> 00:31:14,100
<font color="yellow">You must have read my mind.</font>

468
00:31:14,100 --> 00:31:17,590
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry, Sir. I should have been more careful.</font>

469
00:31:18,590 --> 00:31:20,390
<font color="yellow">I just met Gi Tan.</font>

470
00:31:20,990 --> 00:31:22,290
<font color="yellow">It's not your fault.</font>

471
00:31:23,590 --> 00:31:24,680
<font color="yellow">It was just because...</font>

472
00:31:24,680 --> 00:31:27,200
<font color="yellow">his moves were a bit smarter than ours.</font>

473
00:31:27,200 --> 00:31:28,490
<font color="yellow">It is my fault.</font>

474
00:31:29,490 --> 00:31:31,970
<font color="yellow">I will do anything for you to receive...</font>

475
00:31:31,970 --> 00:31:33,660
<font color="yellow">a judgment of acquittal.</font>

476
00:31:38,220 --> 00:31:40,490
<font color="yellow">I also let my guard down, too.</font>

477
00:31:41,660 --> 00:31:45,590
<font color="yellow">We can't do this together if you continue to blame yourself.</font>

478
00:31:56,120 --> 00:31:57,120
<font color="yellow">Honey.</font>

479
00:32:08,390 --> 00:32:10,590
<font color="yellow">I am sorry that I worried you.</font>

480
00:32:11,590 --> 00:32:13,090
<font color="yellow">I have something to say to you.</font>

481
00:32:14,020 --> 00:32:15,020
<font color="yellow">Let's talk.</font>

482
00:32:37,990 --> 00:32:39,020
<font color="yellow">I have...</font>

483
00:32:40,090 --> 00:32:42,590
<font color="yellow">advised and warned you many times...</font>

484
00:32:43,020 --> 00:32:44,660
<font color="yellow">not to cheat in any way.</font>

485
00:32:46,590 --> 00:32:47,660
<font color="yellow">I have...</font>

486
00:32:48,290 --> 00:32:49,390
<font color="yellow">nothing to say.</font>

487
00:32:51,560 --> 00:32:52,590
<font color="yellow">What is...</font>

488
00:32:53,920 --> 00:32:55,460
<font color="yellow">your relationship...</font>

489
00:32:56,120 --> 00:32:57,620
<font color="yellow">with Chae Ryung?</font>

490
00:33:00,790 --> 00:33:02,120
<font color="yellow">You must know...</font>

491
00:33:02,490 --> 00:33:04,290
<font color="yellow">why I am asking.</font>

492
00:33:06,690 --> 00:33:08,560
<font color="yellow">It is nothing like...</font>

493
00:33:08,560 --> 00:33:11,020
<font color="yellow">what you think it is.</font>

494
00:33:14,390 --> 00:33:15,390
<font color="yellow">Open this.</font>

495
00:33:28,760 --> 00:33:29,860
<font color="yellow">What will you do...</font>

496
00:33:31,190 --> 00:33:33,190
<font color="yellow">with Chae Ryung?</font>

497
00:33:36,490 --> 00:33:37,990
<font color="yellow">Now that I know she's a traitor,</font>

498
00:33:39,290 --> 00:33:40,720
<font color="yellow">I'll use her for my benefits.</font>

499
00:33:41,860 --> 00:33:42,890
<font color="yellow">For your benefits?</font>

500
00:33:43,590 --> 00:33:45,020
<font color="yellow">If we use her well,</font>

501
00:33:45,860 --> 00:33:48,660
<font color="yellow">she will give us a lot of benefits, too.</font>

502
00:33:53,860 --> 00:33:54,860
<font color="yellow">This is bad.</font>

503
00:33:55,190 --> 00:33:57,260
<font color="yellow">The independent prosecutor act has come into effect.</font>

504
00:33:57,260 --> 00:33:58,560
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

505
00:33:58,560 --> 00:33:59,620
<font color="yellow">The independent prosecutor act?</font>

506
00:34:01,090 --> 00:34:03,860
<font color="yellow">The independent prosecutor act has come into effect...</font>

507
00:34:03,860 --> 00:34:08,560
<font color="yellow">regarding Mayor Byun's violation of election law.</font>

508
00:34:08,560 --> 00:34:12,090
<font color="yellow">National Assembly's Committee on Ethics decided...</font>

509
00:34:12,090 --> 00:34:13,920
<font color="yellow">to put this into effect...</font>

510
00:34:13,920 --> 00:34:16,860
<font color="yellow">to relieve the people's suspicions on corrupt politicians.</font>

511
00:34:18,590 --> 00:34:21,530
<font color="yellow">What happens after the act has gone effective?</font>

512
00:34:21,530 --> 00:34:22,860
<font color="yellow">The chairman of the National Assembly...</font>

513
00:34:22,860 --> 00:34:24,430
<font color="yellow">makes a request to the president.</font>

514
00:34:24,430 --> 00:34:26,680
<font color="yellow">Then a special prosecutor is recommended among lawyers...</font>

515
00:34:26,680 --> 00:34:28,580
<font color="yellow">of Korean Bar Association.</font>

516
00:34:28,580 --> 00:34:29,890
<font color="yellow">The tides are high,</font>

517
00:34:30,390 --> 00:34:32,190
<font color="yellow">so there will be many big fish.</font>

518
00:34:32,560 --> 00:34:34,590
<font color="yellow">It's not small enough for Il Jae to cover,</font>

519
00:34:34,590 --> 00:34:36,560
<font color="yellow">so Jae Man will step up.</font>

520
00:34:37,790 --> 00:34:40,090
<font color="yellow">What kind of a man is the chairman?</font>

521
00:34:40,590 --> 00:34:42,880
<font color="yellow">He's known as an honest and an upright man.</font>

522
00:34:42,880 --> 00:34:45,990
<font color="yellow">He wasn't on good terms with Jae Man since they were representatives.</font>

523
00:34:45,990 --> 00:34:47,860
<font color="yellow">If Jae Man decides to step in,</font>

524
00:34:48,760 --> 00:34:50,490
<font color="yellow">he'll approach the chairman.</font>

525
00:34:50,990 --> 00:34:53,160
<font color="yellow">Do you have any connections?</font>

526
00:34:53,160 --> 00:34:54,590
<font color="yellow">I can ask the Chinese ambassador.</font>

527
00:34:55,390 --> 00:34:57,370
<font color="yellow">He can get him to have a meal with me.</font>

528
00:34:57,370 --> 00:35:00,780
<font color="yellow">Right, there was the Chinese ambassador.</font>

529
00:35:00,780 --> 00:35:03,620
<font color="yellow">Why don't we eat Chinese tonight?</font>

530
00:35:08,460 --> 00:35:09,790
<font color="yellow">(Father)</font>

531
00:35:13,590 --> 00:35:14,770
<font color="yellow">Welcome.</font>

532
00:35:14,770 --> 00:35:17,580
<font color="yellow">Chairman got here a bit early because there wasn't much traffic.</font>

533
00:35:17,580 --> 00:35:18,620
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

534
00:35:19,490 --> 00:35:21,750
<font color="yellow">Please tell the ambassador that I will...</font>

535
00:35:21,750 --> 00:35:22,970
<font color="yellow">thank him myself.</font>

536
00:35:22,970 --> 00:35:24,820
<font color="yellow">Sure. Go ahead.</font>

537
00:35:32,790 --> 00:35:33,890
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

538
00:35:34,860 --> 00:35:36,060
<font color="yellow">I am Kang Gi Tan.</font>

539
00:35:36,060 --> 00:35:37,090
<font color="yellow">Welcome.</font>

540
00:35:37,690 --> 00:35:41,560
<font color="yellow">I've heard about you from Ambassador Wang.</font>

541
00:35:41,920 --> 00:35:43,080
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry that I'm late.</font>

542
00:35:43,080 --> 00:35:44,340
<font color="yellow">It's fine.</font>

543
00:35:44,340 --> 00:35:46,860
<font color="yellow">I'm a bit too meticulous, that's all.</font>

544
00:35:54,290 --> 00:35:58,190
<font color="yellow">It's been a while, Mr Hwang.</font>

545
00:35:58,760 --> 00:35:59,790
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

546
00:36:00,190 --> 00:36:01,360
<font color="yellow">Sure.</font>

547
00:36:03,660 --> 00:36:07,620
<font color="yellow">I love how straightforward you are.</font>

548
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:11,490
<font color="yellow">Yes, let's meet there.</font>

549
00:36:12,990 --> 00:36:13,990
<font color="yellow">Sure.</font>

550
00:36:18,090 --> 00:36:19,370
<font color="yellow">Will he meet you?</font>

551
00:36:19,370 --> 00:36:20,390
<font color="yellow">We're meeting...</font>

552
00:36:20,760 --> 00:36:22,620
<font color="yellow">at Buyonggak in two hours.</font>

553
00:36:23,190 --> 00:36:26,000
<font color="yellow">Can you persuade Chairman Kim?</font>

554
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:29,100
<font color="yellow">You two were never on good terms since National Assembly days.</font>

555
00:36:29,100 --> 00:36:30,920
<font color="yellow">This is possible because he's my enemy.</font>

556
00:36:32,290 --> 00:36:33,860
<font color="yellow">I know what he likes.</font>

557
00:36:34,590 --> 00:36:38,490
<font color="yellow">I know everything from his taste to his likes and dislikes.</font>

558
00:36:38,990 --> 00:36:41,390
<font color="yellow">Whatever we do, we have to stop the independent prosecutor from arising.</font>

559
00:36:41,790 --> 00:36:43,290
<font color="yellow">Please, Mr Hwang.</font>

560
00:36:44,560 --> 00:36:49,030
<font color="yellow">I have to stop him before he meets with the president.</font>

561
00:36:50,660 --> 00:36:52,090
<font color="yellow">Tonight is...</font>

562
00:36:52,090 --> 00:36:53,720
<font color="yellow">our final chance.</font>

563
00:37:02,290 --> 00:37:03,760
<font color="yellow">This is it, Father.</font>

564
00:37:03,760 --> 00:37:04,790
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

565
00:37:17,490 --> 00:37:18,560
<font color="yellow">Father.</font>

566
00:37:21,920 --> 00:37:24,590
<font color="yellow">Chairman said he had to go to the Blue House early in the morning,</font>

567
00:37:25,290 --> 00:37:27,120
<font color="yellow">so he asked me to go instead.</font>

568
00:37:27,460 --> 00:37:30,760
<font color="yellow">Have a seat. We've already ordered.</font>

569
00:37:40,690 --> 00:37:42,820
<font color="yellow">The independent prosecutor will be appointed as scheduled,</font>

570
00:37:43,860 --> 00:37:46,920
<font color="yellow">and someone from our side will be appointed.</font>

571
00:37:48,990 --> 00:37:50,030
<font color="yellow">After this,</font>

572
00:37:51,660 --> 00:37:53,690
<font color="yellow">Il Jae will receive a sentence of imprisonment.</font>

573
00:37:54,390 --> 00:37:55,760
<font color="yellow">The problem comes after.</font>

574
00:37:56,220 --> 00:37:57,290
<font color="yellow">What I want is...</font>

575
00:37:58,220 --> 00:38:01,220
<font color="yellow">to completely ostracise Il Jae from this society.</font>

576
00:38:01,220 --> 00:38:02,560
<font color="yellow">Hey, Gi Tan.</font>

577
00:38:02,560 --> 00:38:05,190
<font color="yellow">I've been giving it a thought on...</font>

578
00:38:06,290 --> 00:38:08,460
<font color="yellow">why you couldn't just abandon him.</font>

579
00:38:16,290 --> 00:38:17,360
<font color="yellow">Maybe...</font>

580
00:38:18,030 --> 00:38:19,390
<font color="yellow">my aunt's death...</font>

581
00:38:20,990 --> 00:38:23,890
<font color="yellow">has something to do with Congresswoman Hwang.</font>

582
00:38:26,990 --> 00:38:30,760
<font color="yellow">I thought that could be the one weakness Il Jae knows about you.</font>

583
00:38:31,490 --> 00:38:32,620
<font color="yellow">Stop speaking nonsense.</font>

584
00:38:33,190 --> 00:38:34,650
<font color="yellow">How dare you?</font>

585
00:38:34,650 --> 00:38:35,660
<font color="yellow">So what?</font>

586
00:38:37,030 --> 00:38:38,030
<font color="yellow">Why...</font>

587
00:38:39,030 --> 00:38:43,030
<font color="yellow">are you here instead of Chairman Kim?</font>

588
00:38:43,860 --> 00:38:45,790
<font color="yellow">If you abandon Il Jae,</font>

589
00:38:47,190 --> 00:38:48,290
<font color="yellow">I will help you...</font>

590
00:38:49,490 --> 00:38:50,620
<font color="yellow">with your presidential election.</font>

591
00:38:56,030 --> 00:38:57,820
<font color="yellow">I have nothing against you.</font>

592
00:38:59,220 --> 00:39:00,990
<font color="yellow">But if we fight because of Il Jae,</font>

593
00:39:01,560 --> 00:39:04,190
<font color="yellow">that will leave us both with great wounds.</font>

594
00:39:05,290 --> 00:39:06,790
<font color="yellow">What you're saying is...</font>

595
00:39:07,590 --> 00:39:09,460
<font color="yellow">that you'll pay me...</font>

596
00:39:09,990 --> 00:39:12,120
<font color="yellow">to control me around.</font>

597
00:39:13,990 --> 00:39:15,630
<font color="yellow">Hey, Mr Kang.</font>

598
00:39:15,630 --> 00:39:19,660
<font color="yellow">I'm the person holding the sword, not the sword itself.</font>

599
00:39:20,290 --> 00:39:22,360
<font color="yellow">If you can offer yourself as a sword,</font>

600
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:24,720
<font color="yellow">I don't think anyone would decline.</font>

601
00:39:25,490 --> 00:39:26,490
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

602
00:39:26,860 --> 00:39:28,660
<font color="yellow">if you want to be my sword,</font>

603
00:39:29,120 --> 00:39:30,190
<font color="yellow">you first...</font>

604
00:39:30,590 --> 00:39:32,290
<font color="yellow">have to let go of Il Jae.</font>

605
00:39:33,390 --> 00:39:38,190
<font color="yellow">You'd have to deal with me after you get rid of him, anyways.</font>

606
00:39:39,030 --> 00:39:40,030
<font color="yellow">Once I have...</font>

607
00:39:40,590 --> 00:39:42,090
<font color="yellow">the presidency,</font>

608
00:39:43,290 --> 00:39:45,220
<font color="yellow">what will happen to you?</font>

609
00:39:47,290 --> 00:39:49,490
<font color="yellow">Revenge will only bring another revenge.</font>

610
00:39:50,360 --> 00:39:51,390
<font color="yellow">But...</font>

611
00:39:51,990 --> 00:39:53,390
<font color="yellow">the revenge I have in mind is...</font>

612
00:39:54,190 --> 00:39:56,690
<font color="yellow">something beyond anything you can imagine.</font>

613
00:39:57,660 --> 00:40:00,620
<font color="yellow">So you should just...</font>

614
00:40:01,290 --> 00:40:02,290
<font color="yellow">stop here.</font>

615
00:40:04,090 --> 00:40:05,490
<font color="yellow">We're beating around the bush.</font>

616
00:40:06,490 --> 00:40:09,560
<font color="yellow">I don't care if I'm the sword. My opponent won't change.</font>

617
00:40:10,660 --> 00:40:11,990
<font color="yellow">I just hope...</font>

618
00:40:13,560 --> 00:40:16,360
<font color="yellow">you won't get hurt by the tip of the sword.</font>

619
00:40:31,920 --> 00:40:35,360
<font color="yellow">Father, will the independent prosecutor act really be effective?</font>

620
00:40:37,390 --> 00:40:39,290
<font color="yellow">I'll hold a press conference tomorrow.</font>

621
00:40:40,590 --> 00:40:42,590
<font color="yellow">Call the press.</font>

622
00:40:43,490 --> 00:40:44,620
<font color="yellow">For what?</font>

623
00:40:54,190 --> 00:40:55,640
<font color="yellow">From what I heard,</font>

624
00:40:55,640 --> 00:40:57,860
<font color="yellow">Jae Man and Il Jae are as good as over.</font>

625
00:40:59,290 --> 00:41:01,030
<font color="yellow">I guess blood is thicker than water.</font>

626
00:41:01,760 --> 00:41:02,760
<font color="yellow">By the way,</font>

627
00:41:03,190 --> 00:41:05,030
<font color="yellow">what you said to Jae Man...</font>

628
00:41:05,590 --> 00:41:06,720
<font color="yellow">about abandoning Il Jae...</font>

629
00:41:07,290 --> 00:41:09,820
<font color="yellow">Were you really going to help his presidential election?</font>

630
00:41:10,560 --> 00:41:12,590
<font color="yellow">The wrong president will bring the country down.</font>

631
00:41:13,560 --> 00:41:14,920
<font color="yellow">Getting my revenge is important,</font>

632
00:41:16,460 --> 00:41:18,290
<font color="yellow">but I will never help anyone like him.</font>

633
00:41:22,990 --> 00:41:24,260
<font color="yellow">You're a patriot.</font>

634
00:41:27,790 --> 00:41:30,960
<font color="yellow">A special inspection was requested.</font>

635
00:41:32,160 --> 00:41:33,190
<font color="yellow">I, Hwang Jae Man,</font>

636
00:41:34,160 --> 00:41:37,360
<font color="yellow">strongly support the need for an investigation...</font>

637
00:41:38,120 --> 00:41:41,960
<font color="yellow">to find out if Mayor Byun Il Jae really did...</font>

638
00:41:42,620 --> 00:41:44,360
<font color="yellow">violate any election laws.</font>

639
00:41:45,490 --> 00:41:48,090
<font color="yellow">Do you believe he's innocent?</font>

640
00:41:48,090 --> 00:41:49,290
<font color="yellow">Of course, I do.</font>

641
00:41:49,790 --> 00:41:52,190
<font color="yellow">Why did you arrange this press conference?</font>

642
00:41:52,890 --> 00:41:55,160
<font color="yellow">If he is to lead Seoul Metropolitan City,</font>

643
00:41:55,860 --> 00:41:57,690
<font color="yellow">I believe that...</font>

644
00:41:58,320 --> 00:42:01,960
<font color="yellow">he must be cleared of all suspicions and doubts.</font>

645
00:42:02,890 --> 00:42:06,690
<font color="yellow">This is what my son-in-law, Byun Il Jae, wants.</font>

646
00:42:09,390 --> 00:42:12,960
<font color="yellow">He can't divert the current, so he's floating a boat.</font>

647
00:42:12,960 --> 00:42:14,860
<font color="yellow">Mr Hwang's onboard now.</font>

648
00:42:15,590 --> 00:42:17,260
<font color="yellow">We can sink them both.</font>

649
00:42:18,490 --> 00:42:20,320
<font color="yellow">Now that he got involved,</font>

650
00:42:20,320 --> 00:42:22,260
<font color="yellow">it'll be more than just a raft.</font>

651
00:42:23,890 --> 00:42:26,890
<font color="yellow">Is Lawyer Oh going to be named the lead investigator today?</font>

652
00:42:27,960 --> 00:42:29,320
<font color="yellow">She'll be at the Blue House now.</font>

653
00:42:29,690 --> 00:42:31,490
<font color="yellow">The president will give her the certificate.</font>

654
00:42:47,960 --> 00:42:50,190
<font color="yellow">Lawyer Oh is the special investigator?</font>

655
00:42:50,620 --> 00:42:53,160
<font color="yellow">The Bar Association must have recommended her.</font>

656
00:42:53,160 --> 00:42:54,790
<font color="yellow">I think Lawyer Min's behind it.</font>

657
00:42:56,690 --> 00:42:58,890
<font color="yellow">Their witnesses will be Cho Cham...</font>

658
00:42:58,890 --> 00:43:00,790
<font color="yellow">and the antique dealer.</font>

659
00:43:01,190 --> 00:43:02,490
<font color="yellow">How did Gi Tan...</font>

660
00:43:02,990 --> 00:43:05,420
<font color="yellow">get his hands on the recording?</font>

661
00:43:07,860 --> 00:43:08,890
<font color="yellow">Do you think...</font>

662
00:43:09,990 --> 00:43:11,260
<font color="yellow">there's a spy?</font>

663
00:43:17,160 --> 00:43:18,290
<font color="yellow">Huaping...</font>

664
00:43:18,860 --> 00:43:21,590
<font color="yellow">had all sorts of listening devices we'd never seen before.</font>

665
00:43:23,220 --> 00:43:26,290
<font color="yellow">I should have been more careful. This is my fault.</font>

666
00:43:26,690 --> 00:43:28,690
<font color="yellow">Apologising won't change anything.</font>

667
00:43:29,290 --> 00:43:32,190
<font color="yellow">Why did you even start what you couldn't handle...</font>

668
00:43:32,190 --> 00:43:33,290
<font color="yellow">It was my call.</font>

669
00:43:33,890 --> 00:43:36,390
<font color="yellow">Don't take it out on her.</font>

670
00:43:37,960 --> 00:43:40,090
<font color="yellow">Call me as your witness.</font>

671
00:43:43,320 --> 00:43:44,890
<font color="yellow">Would you really do that?</font>

672
00:43:46,360 --> 00:43:47,520
<font color="yellow">That won't be necessary.</font>

673
00:43:48,260 --> 00:43:49,370
<font color="yellow">Honey.</font>

674
00:43:49,370 --> 00:43:52,260
<font color="yellow">If I say Gi Tan bribed me into helping him,</font>

675
00:43:52,260 --> 00:43:54,490
<font color="yellow">you won't need any more witnesses.</font>

676
00:43:55,090 --> 00:43:57,890
<font color="yellow">We need to find a way to silence Cho Cham.</font>

677
00:43:57,890 --> 00:44:00,580
<font color="yellow">The problem is that we can't.</font>

678
00:44:00,580 --> 00:44:03,490
<font color="yellow">If all else fails, we can get rid of him.</font>

679
00:44:05,690 --> 00:44:08,060
<font color="yellow">Don't say something like that.</font>

680
00:44:08,960 --> 00:44:11,260
<font color="yellow">It just came out. I'm frustrated, that's all.</font>

681
00:44:12,590 --> 00:44:14,840
<font color="yellow">Don't say what you don't mean.</font>

682
00:44:14,840 --> 00:44:17,090
<font color="yellow">You'll become mayor once this is all over.</font>

683
00:44:17,890 --> 00:44:21,990
<font color="yellow">If you take the stand, it could backfire.</font>

684
00:44:22,620 --> 00:44:24,090
<font color="yellow">Don't give a statement.</font>

685
00:44:26,160 --> 00:44:28,060
<font color="yellow">Who will defend me?</font>

686
00:44:28,760 --> 00:44:31,160
<font color="yellow">Lawyer Nam Ji Cheol, a previous High Court judge.</font>

687
00:44:32,160 --> 00:44:34,520
<font color="yellow">Set up a meeting right away.</font>

688
00:44:34,960 --> 00:44:35,990
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

689
00:44:45,690 --> 00:44:47,790
<font color="yellow">She volunteered to be a witness.</font>

690
00:44:47,790 --> 00:44:48,990
<font color="yellow">Why did you refuse?</font>

691
00:44:49,690 --> 00:44:50,690
<font color="yellow">Out of concern.</font>

692
00:44:52,620 --> 00:44:55,590
<font color="yellow">You can't worry about her when you're in this mess.</font>

693
00:44:56,490 --> 00:44:58,890
<font color="yellow">I'm worried about the trial, not about her.</font>

694
00:44:58,890 --> 00:45:00,120
<font color="yellow">I don't trust her.</font>

695
00:45:02,290 --> 00:45:03,890
<font color="yellow">If she takes the stand...</font>

696
00:45:03,890 --> 00:45:06,790
<font color="yellow">and betrays me, then I will definitely go down.</font>

697
00:45:09,320 --> 00:45:12,220
<font color="yellow">I thought you were defending her.</font>

698
00:45:14,060 --> 00:45:16,090
<font color="yellow">We need to silence Cho Cham.</font>

699
00:45:16,620 --> 00:45:18,690
<font color="yellow">The whole trial hinges on that.</font>

700
00:45:22,890 --> 00:45:24,290
<font color="yellow">(Ok Chae Ryung)</font>

701
00:45:25,990 --> 00:45:27,990
<font color="yellow">You meet with Lawyer Nam for me.</font>

702
00:45:28,490 --> 00:45:29,490
<font color="yellow">Honey.</font>

703
00:45:29,890 --> 00:45:31,350
<font color="yellow">Who called you?</font>

704
00:45:31,350 --> 00:45:33,490
<font color="yellow">I'll explain later. Get going.</font>

705
00:45:41,520 --> 00:45:42,590
<font color="yellow">(Ok Chae Ryung)</font>

706
00:45:52,090 --> 00:45:55,760
<font color="yellow">What you said earlier. It didn't sound like a joke.</font>

707
00:45:57,220 --> 00:45:59,160
<font color="yellow">That is the only option...</font>

708
00:45:59,790 --> 00:46:00,960
<font color="yellow">we have.</font>

709
00:46:06,590 --> 00:46:07,860
<font color="yellow">We must kill him.</font>

710
00:46:09,990 --> 00:46:12,490
<font color="yellow">He's in a cell. It won't be easy.</font>

711
00:46:15,390 --> 00:46:16,890
<font color="yellow">Insulin shots.</font>

712
00:46:17,960 --> 00:46:18,990
<font color="yellow">Insulin?</font>

713
00:46:19,860 --> 00:46:22,190
<font color="yellow">Cho Cham has diabetes.</font>

714
00:46:23,060 --> 00:46:24,470
<font color="yellow">If he's injected with...</font>

715
00:46:24,470 --> 00:46:26,590
<font color="yellow">potassium chloride instead of insulin,</font>

716
00:46:27,220 --> 00:46:28,760
<font color="yellow">his heart will go into overdrive.</font>

717
00:46:29,190 --> 00:46:31,620
<font color="yellow">It's a perfect crime.</font>

718
00:46:34,590 --> 00:46:37,990
<font color="yellow">You found a way out of this trial.</font>

719
00:46:42,490 --> 00:46:43,690
<font color="yellow">I wish you victory.</font>

720
00:46:54,120 --> 00:46:56,690
<font color="yellow">Il Jae is going further and further.</font>

721
00:46:57,120 --> 00:46:58,780
<font color="yellow">He's trying to kill a witness, too?</font>

722
00:46:58,780 --> 00:47:00,960
<font color="yellow">You have to protect him.</font>

723
00:47:00,960 --> 00:47:02,390
<font color="yellow">We can do that.</font>

724
00:47:03,390 --> 00:47:04,490
<font color="yellow">Thank you, Chae Ryung.</font>

725
00:47:05,220 --> 00:47:06,290
<font color="yellow">Mr Moon.</font>

726
00:47:07,690 --> 00:47:08,690
<font color="yellow">During the trial,</font>

727
00:47:09,260 --> 00:47:11,090
<font color="yellow">put me on the stand as your witness.</font>

728
00:47:12,260 --> 00:47:13,290
<font color="yellow">Chae Ryung.</font>

729
00:47:13,290 --> 00:47:14,890
<font color="yellow">If I give a statement,</font>

730
00:47:15,290 --> 00:47:16,960
<font color="yellow">you will definitely win.</font>

731
00:47:16,960 --> 00:47:20,230
<font color="yellow">That means you'd have to admit to criminal activity.</font>

732
00:47:20,230 --> 00:47:22,230
<font color="yellow">I'll go to prison and do time.</font>

733
00:47:22,230 --> 00:47:23,620
<font color="yellow">That doesn't scare me.</font>

734
00:47:25,790 --> 00:47:29,090
<font color="yellow">If Huaping finds out you're alive, your life will be in danger...</font>

735
00:47:29,490 --> 00:47:31,190
<font color="yellow">whether or not you're behind bars.</font>

736
00:47:31,760 --> 00:47:32,790
<font color="yellow">This is a chance...</font>

737
00:47:33,360 --> 00:47:35,120
<font color="yellow">to clear my name.</font>

738
00:47:35,760 --> 00:47:36,980
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

739
00:47:36,980 --> 00:47:39,590
<font color="yellow">Il Jae took the MK2 vaccine.</font>

740
00:47:40,290 --> 00:47:42,890
<font color="yellow">If my statement helps cancel his election,</font>

741
00:47:43,360 --> 00:47:45,390
<font color="yellow">nothing would please the Huaping more.</font>

742
00:47:46,690 --> 00:47:47,960
<font color="yellow">What if they don't forgive you?</font>

743
00:47:49,420 --> 00:47:50,590
<font color="yellow">I'll accept my fate.</font>

744
00:47:51,290 --> 00:47:54,160
<font color="yellow">I can't spend the rest of my life a fugitive.</font>

745
00:47:56,120 --> 00:47:57,520
<font color="yellow">I know my boss.</font>

746
00:47:57,990 --> 00:48:00,990
<font color="yellow">Trust me. Put me on the stand.</font>

747
00:48:04,990 --> 00:48:06,790
<font color="yellow">(Prison)</font>

748
00:48:11,960 --> 00:48:14,100
<font color="yellow">Once a day, the prison doctor...</font>

749
00:48:14,100 --> 00:48:16,390
<font color="yellow">will administer the insulin shot.</font>

750
00:48:16,960 --> 00:48:20,520
<font color="yellow">I told the doctor to be careful, so they won't be able...</font>

751
00:48:20,520 --> 00:48:22,290
<font color="yellow">to switch the syringes that easily.</font>

752
00:48:24,490 --> 00:48:26,490
<font color="yellow">When he isn't with the doctor,</font>

753
00:48:26,490 --> 00:48:28,690
<font color="yellow">the prison guards will watch him around the clock.</font>

754
00:48:29,490 --> 00:48:31,250
<font color="yellow">Don't worry.</font>

755
00:48:31,250 --> 00:48:34,760
<font color="yellow">I explained it all to the witness and told him to be wary.</font>

756
00:48:34,760 --> 00:48:35,990
<font color="yellow">You don't have to worry.</font>

757
00:48:37,790 --> 00:48:41,120
<font color="yellow">If they're caught switching the syringes before the trial,</font>

758
00:48:41,760 --> 00:48:45,030
<font color="yellow">we can add attempted murder to Il Jae's list of charges.</font>

759
00:48:45,030 --> 00:48:46,390
<font color="yellow">You're very thorough.</font>

760
00:48:46,890 --> 00:48:48,860
<font color="yellow">You're a great partner.</font>

761
00:48:53,790 --> 00:48:54,890
<font color="yellow">Are we done?</font>

762
00:48:55,320 --> 00:48:57,760
<font color="yellow">- Yes.
-  Sir, your next appointment...</font>

763
00:48:57,760 --> 00:48:59,090
<font color="yellow">Cancel it.</font>

764
00:48:59,520 --> 00:49:00,860
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon.</font>

765
00:49:00,860 --> 00:49:02,990
<font color="yellow">Stay for dinner and a chat.</font>

766
00:49:05,590 --> 00:49:08,420
<font color="yellow">Sorry, but I have to meet a client.</font>

767
00:49:08,420 --> 00:49:09,490
<font color="yellow">Why are you lying?</font>

768
00:49:11,390 --> 00:49:13,860
<font color="yellow">You were on the phone saying you'd go straight home.</font>

769
00:49:18,590 --> 00:49:20,120
<font color="yellow">I'll be honest, then.</font>

770
00:49:20,790 --> 00:49:24,120
<font color="yellow">Joining you for a meal would make me feel uncomfortable.</font>

771
00:49:26,060 --> 00:49:27,190
<font color="yellow">Would the reason for that...</font>

772
00:49:28,320 --> 00:49:29,520
<font color="yellow">be Do Gun Woo?</font>

773
00:49:35,420 --> 00:49:37,390
<font color="yellow">If so, then I really can't give in.</font>

774
00:49:38,620 --> 00:49:40,360
<font color="yellow">Tell the chef to prepare his special.</font>

775
00:49:40,690 --> 00:49:41,760
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

776
00:50:00,160 --> 00:50:02,890
<font color="yellow">- As a witness at the trial...
-  Is Gun Woo very jealous?</font>

777
00:50:05,690 --> 00:50:08,390
<font color="yellow">Please don't ask personal questions.</font>

778
00:50:10,390 --> 00:50:12,890
<font color="yellow">- I won't.
-  At the trial,</font>

779
00:50:13,490 --> 00:50:16,760
<font color="yellow">we'll add one more witness that Il Jae won't even expect.</font>

780
00:50:16,760 --> 00:50:18,220
<font color="yellow">Someone to incriminate him.</font>

781
00:50:19,590 --> 00:50:21,890
<font color="yellow">That's our hidden card.</font>

782
00:50:22,490 --> 00:50:23,590
<font color="yellow">Who is it?</font>

783
00:50:33,390 --> 00:50:36,220
<font color="yellow">Chae Ryung will be our witness?</font>

784
00:50:37,320 --> 00:50:40,320
<font color="yellow">I need you to keep it from the chairman until the trial.</font>

785
00:50:42,760 --> 00:50:43,790
<font color="yellow">Chae Ryung's...</font>

786
00:50:44,490 --> 00:50:46,790
<font color="yellow">working for Il Jae as our spy.</font>

787
00:50:48,860 --> 00:50:51,290
<font color="yellow">Then this whole corruption case...</font>

788
00:50:51,290 --> 00:50:52,520
<font color="yellow">It was her design.</font>

789
00:50:54,790 --> 00:50:58,790
<font color="yellow">You and the chairman cut and sewed along the lines.</font>

790
00:51:00,860 --> 00:51:01,890
<font color="yellow">Thanks to her,</font>

791
00:51:02,490 --> 00:51:04,060
<font color="yellow">we have a prison uniform...</font>

792
00:51:04,860 --> 00:51:06,390
<font color="yellow">that will fit Il Jae perfectly.</font>

793
00:51:09,390 --> 00:51:10,690
<font color="yellow">Who's that hidden card?</font>

794
00:51:12,620 --> 00:51:15,890
<font color="yellow">The witness asked to remain unknown until the day of the trial.</font>

795
00:51:16,420 --> 00:51:17,860
<font color="yellow">I can't say any more.</font>

796
00:51:18,320 --> 00:51:19,790
<font color="yellow">We're on the same side.</font>

797
00:51:20,160 --> 00:51:23,360
<font color="yellow">I'm a lawyer and a specially appointed investigator.</font>

798
00:51:23,820 --> 00:51:25,790
<font color="yellow">I have to protect the witnesses.</font>

799
00:51:27,790 --> 00:51:29,790
<font color="yellow">Now, I'm too curious to eat.</font>

800
00:51:32,020 --> 00:51:33,690
<font color="yellow">I love meat.</font>

801
00:51:41,690 --> 00:51:43,090
<font color="yellow">You're pretty when you smile.</font>

802
00:51:44,490 --> 00:51:47,910
<font color="yellow">- Pardon?
-  It's not a personal question.</font>

803
00:51:47,910 --> 00:51:49,060
<font color="yellow">Can I say how I feel?</font>

804
00:51:51,860 --> 00:51:54,990
<font color="yellow">Your smile makes me feel better.</font>

805
00:51:57,160 --> 00:51:59,090
<font color="yellow">I'd like to see it more often.</font>

806
00:52:00,190 --> 00:52:01,360
<font color="yellow">Is that too rude?</font>

807
00:52:02,590 --> 00:52:03,690
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

808
00:52:04,760 --> 00:52:05,890
<font color="yellow">I guess it was.</font>

809
00:52:08,120 --> 00:52:09,190
<font color="yellow">I'll buy you a drink.</font>

810
00:52:09,520 --> 00:52:12,060
<font color="yellow">- What?
-  I was rude.</font>

811
00:52:12,390 --> 00:52:14,390
<font color="yellow">I'll buy a drink to apologise.</font>

812
00:52:16,390 --> 00:52:18,390
<font color="yellow">I know I make you feel uncomfortable.</font>

813
00:52:18,990 --> 00:52:22,390
<font color="yellow">I'm trying to get close to you, so don't shoot me down yet.</font>

814
00:52:33,390 --> 00:52:34,990
<font color="yellow">He's with her again.</font>

815
00:52:36,060 --> 00:52:39,070
<font color="yellow">Have you ever seen him smile like that?</font>

816
00:52:39,070 --> 00:52:40,090
<font color="yellow">Never.</font>

817
00:52:40,990 --> 00:52:42,060
<font color="yellow">Do you think...</font>

818
00:52:42,590 --> 00:52:43,820
<font color="yellow">they're dating?</font>

819
00:52:55,690 --> 00:52:57,560
<font color="yellow">Why are you calling me?</font>

820
00:52:58,120 --> 00:53:01,190
<font color="yellow">Explain why Soo Yeon is having dinner with Gi Tan.</font>

821
00:53:03,960 --> 00:53:05,190
<font color="yellow">Why are you asking me that?</font>

822
00:53:05,690 --> 00:53:07,820
<font color="yellow">You and she have sort of a relationship.</font>

823
00:53:08,490 --> 00:53:11,170
<font color="yellow">Did you know they were meeting often?</font>

824
00:53:11,170 --> 00:53:12,290
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

825
00:53:12,620 --> 00:53:13,620
<font color="yellow">Really?</font>

826
00:53:14,160 --> 00:53:17,390
<font color="yellow">They're discussing business, so don't get involved.</font>

827
00:53:18,090 --> 00:53:21,560
<font color="yellow">Why would they be smiling while discussing business?</font>

828
00:53:21,560 --> 00:53:23,120
<font color="yellow">I'm too busy to talk about this.</font>

829
00:53:35,360 --> 00:53:36,360
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

830
00:53:37,860 --> 00:53:40,990
<font color="yellow">You avoided me when I invited you out for dinner.</font>

831
00:53:41,390 --> 00:53:43,600
<font color="yellow">Now, you're too busy grinning to eat.</font>

832
00:53:43,600 --> 00:53:45,660
<font color="yellow">It's a post-meeting dinner.</font>

833
00:53:45,660 --> 00:53:46,870
<font color="yellow">Stay out of it.</font>

834
00:53:46,870 --> 00:53:47,890
<font color="yellow">A meeting?</font>

835
00:53:49,060 --> 00:53:50,360
<font color="yellow">I should go.</font>

836
00:53:51,690 --> 00:53:52,690
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon.</font>

837
00:53:53,090 --> 00:53:54,520
<font color="yellow">I have a trial to prepare for.</font>

838
00:53:55,190 --> 00:53:57,290
<font color="yellow">Thanks for the meal. The next one's on me.</font>

839
00:53:59,190 --> 00:54:00,370
<font color="yellow">Soo Yeon.</font>

840
00:54:00,370 --> 00:54:02,260
<font color="yellow">- You can't go.
-  Let go.</font>

841
00:54:03,120 --> 00:54:05,160
<font color="yellow">Let's have a meeting. Right now.</font>

842
00:54:05,160 --> 00:54:06,340
<font color="yellow">Shin Young.</font>

843
00:54:06,340 --> 00:54:08,120
<font color="yellow">We're business partners.</font>

844
00:54:09,260 --> 00:54:10,390
<font color="yellow">Let's have a meeting.</font>

845
00:54:11,190 --> 00:54:12,290
<font color="yellow">Then we can eat.</font>

846
00:54:17,190 --> 00:54:20,260
<font color="yellow">Are you really going to kill Cho Cham?</font>

847
00:54:20,260 --> 00:54:21,590
<font color="yellow">No fool...</font>

848
00:54:21,960 --> 00:54:24,690
<font color="yellow">would kill a witness right before a trial.</font>

849
00:54:25,620 --> 00:54:26,820
<font color="yellow">Then why...</font>

850
00:54:28,290 --> 00:54:31,390
<font color="yellow">I gave Chae Ryung false information.</font>

851
00:54:33,390 --> 00:54:34,660
<font color="yellow">I will...</font>

852
00:54:35,090 --> 00:54:37,520
<font color="yellow">make noise in the east and then attack from the west.</font>

853
00:54:40,060 --> 00:54:43,090
<font color="yellow">While Gi Tan is obsessing over the syringe,</font>

854
00:54:45,190 --> 00:54:47,820
<font color="yellow">I need you to travel to the US.</font>

855
